<p><strong>Military Panel: </strong>The role of the military on the international level in the 21st century.</p>
<p><em>These US service men between them have active-duty experience just about everywhere around the world both on land and sea, serving in various wars and on bases across the globe. All have now retired from active duty and now working in various technological, educational, and leadership positions in Idaho. Among our guests are a previous West Point instructor, fighter pilot, and an awardee of the Purple Heart.</em></p>
